snippet.title: New World: Aeternum - Gameplay Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official gameplay launch trailer for New World: Aeternum.
 
The mysterious island is within reach, but the cost of the voyage could be deadly. As demon hordes rise and secrets are revealed, only true adventurers can survive. Will you join the fight and fulfill your destiny? Aeternum awaits!

Buy Now:

Xbox https://bit.ly/4bQgT8a
Steam https://bit.ly/4bIY2ff
